# hello-webpresso

Verifies wp setup is complete.

## Steps

1. Confirm `.agent/skills/hello-webpresso/SKILL.md` exists
2. Confirm `wp compile` has been run (check `.claude/skills/` exists)
3. Say: "webpresso is ready. Run `wp compile` to sync to all IDEs."
